Source: flowcoin
Section: net
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Haruki Tanaka <haruki@flowcoin.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 12),
               cmake (>= 3.20),
               g++ (>= 10),
               pkg-config,
               libc6-dev
Standards-Version: 4.5.1
Homepage: https://flowcoin.org
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/flowcoin/flowcoin.git

Package: flowcoind
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: FlowCoin daemon - Keccak-256d Proof-of-Work blockchain
 FlowCoin is a Keccak-256d Proof-of-Work cryptocurrency.
 This package contains the full node daemon (flowcoind),
 the CLI client (flowcoin-cli), and the offline transaction
 utility (flowcoin-tx).

Package: flowcoin-cli
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: FlowCoin CLI - command line RPC client
 Lightweight command-line client for communicating with a running
 flowcoind instance via JSON-RPC. Does not include the full node
 daemon or wallet functionality.
